Description: Provides a novel framework to able to automatically
        develop and deploy an accurate Multiple Classifier System based
        on the feature-clustering distribution achieved from an input
        dataset. 'D2MCS' was developed focused on four main aspects:
        (i) the ability to determine an effective method to evaluate
        the independence of features, (ii) the identification of the
        optimal number of feature clusters, (iii) the training and
        tuning of ML models and (iv) the execution of voting schemes to
        combine the outputs of each classifier comprising the Multiple
        Classifier System.
